title: A1466 2013-2015 test enclosure
message:
Hi, First I wanna apologize as I don’t know if this is the right place for this question. I have a few boards a1466 from ranging from 2013-2015 I’m looking to buy a test enclosure I found a few 2013 and A few 2015 Enclosures 
Both seem pretty similar. Are all these board compatible with either of these enclosures ?
By enclosures I mean the case with screen and palest battery.

title: A1466 2013-2015 test enclosure
message: You can interchange 3437 and 00165 boards, in the same test enclosure.

title: A1466 2013-2015 test enclosure
message: Thank you for clearing that up :)
